We’re so excited to share something crispy, bold, and packed with Korean Flavor—Soban’s Korean BBQ Pork Rinds are officially here! 😋🔥

latestPosts.caption:
if you know me, i’m more of a sweet dessert girl and my husband is 100% a chip guy — BUT these Premium Korean Sweet & Spicy Puffs from @soban.kpantry were the perfect middle ground 🍗🌶️ we both couldn’t stop snacking on them.

& as someone who’s probably taste-tested every new Korean snack out there (lol), these definitely make the must try list.

if you really know me… you know i love a good deal — you can find them at all Costco LA stores (including OC!) for just $5.99 until July 3rd 🗓️

perfect for friend hangs, chill nights, or just a solo snack moment 🫶 so run to your nearest Costco now!
